{"tid":853999,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【中美貿易】IMF：全面爆發貿易戰 中國損失將高於美國","createTime":"2018-10-09T04:44:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-09T06:07:18.000Z","uid":79563,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"519419c5de903f5e9bd4cd0ad01372386e39deea","tid":853999,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T04:44:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1539052835880&amp;issue=20181009\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mpfinance.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1539052835880%26issue%3D20181009&d=sZljDrWenY9hBEOu%2BnkSM5Uc5Mn1qk%2F8nAzLhrzJJK4%3D&h=77c86f71\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1539052835880&amp;issue=20181009</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/fin/20181009/s00010/62f66b1506bb54f070c488685006c79b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2F20181009%2Fs00010%2F62f66b1506bb54f070c488685006c79b.jpg&h=1ae5012d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n國際貨幣基金組織(IMF)在一項顯示全球經濟面臨的貿易戰風險的新模型中，模擬了全面爆發中美貿易戰的影響，以及美國威脅對全球汽車徵稅，以及貿易夥伴國出手報復。該模型還包括企業信心下降的影響，信心下降會促使企業削減投資，造成金融條件趨緊。<br />\n<br />\n結果顯示，對美國和中國的影響將特別嚴重，美國2019年GDP將損失逾0.9%，中國則將損失1.6%。<br />\n<br />\n模型亦顯示，當國內生產取代了較高價的進口品時，將會進行調整，但長期而言，美國GDP仍較沒有這些關稅情況下的基本假設情況少了1.0%；中國GDP將比基本假設低了0.5%。"},{"pid":"5a14d81f1abd979e7982dff720b040ee1465c4a4","tid":853999,"uid":24853,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T04:48:05.000Z","msg":"支爆gogogo"},{"pid":"f8c09856694fea594ff7a4022eee935d3c968632","tid":853999,"uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T04:49:27.000Z","msg":"上次歐洲央行個model 話美國損失多d wor"},{"pid":"d625929d5892a7605c327f27715d875bdc96a615","tid":853999,"uid":63909,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T04:50:29.000Z","msg":"IMF條死法國白左ON膠咩咩德一早投咗共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be0d3ca9aaeb33b9fff75